lib.frc1747.motion_profile

Class Parameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • lib.frc1747.motion_profile.Parameters

  • public class Parameters
extends java.lang.Object
    Reasonable default motion profile parameters used with 1747's 2017 robot. All units should match those in the profile follower, and parameters such as DT should match as well. Note that these are for low gear.
    Author:
    Tiger Huang
